Step 1: Start
Step 2: Initialize data segment
Step 3: Declare messages to Display on Screen
Step 4: End Data Segment
Step 5: Initialize Code Segment
Step 6: Assume cs:code, ds:data
Step 7: Start Program
Step 8: Move data to ds
Step 9: Load Message to Display
Step 10: Display Message on Screen
Step 11: Enter Number
Step 12: Store 02 in b1
Step 13: Divide Number by b1
Step 14: Check Remainder
Step 15: If No, Go to Step 18
Step 16: Else load Message Odd to Display
Step 17: Display Message on Screen and Go to Step 20
Step 18: Load Message Even to Display
Step 19: Display Message on Screen
Step 20: End code segment
Step 21: End Program
Step 22: Stop